No. 10-447. Djamel Ameziane, Petitioner v. Barack H. Obama, President of the United States, et al. 562 U.S. 1302, 131 S. Ct. 1673,

179 L. Ed. 2d 644,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 2164. March 21, 2011.

Motion of respondents for leave to file a brief in opposition under seal granted. Motion of petitioner for leave to file a reply brief under seal granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia Circuit denied.

Justice Kagan took no part in the consideration or decision of these motions and this petition.

Same case below, 393 U.S. App. D.C. 123, 620 F.3d 1.
